This is the Debian GNU/Linux package of icom.
This package was put together from sources obtained at:
  http://www.eecis.udel.edu/~mills/resource/icom.tar.gz
by Colin Tuckley <colint@debian.org>
Previous versions were obtained from:
  http://www.eecis.udel.edu/~ntp/ntp_spool/software/icom.tar.gz
by Hamish Moffatt <hamish@debian.org>

